data.description: Great condo located in a quiet but central area of Chula Vista. This second level unit features two bedrooms, two baths, large patio deck with storage.   Floor plan provides privacy for each bedroom, with a bed and bath on each side of the unit, separated by the living room. Unit has just been painted and has new carpet.  Both bedrooms offer great closet space. Primary has walkin closet. In unit washer/dryer will convey. Development features a community pool a one car garage and one assigned parking space. Located just blocks from the 805 and a short distance to grocery store's, coffee shops, dining, retail shops, and so much more.
